lyrics:
[Verse]
Cristina and her loyal friend Ron
Together they'll conquer the world, from dusk till dawn
Through ups and downs, they stand strong
A bond so tight, a love that's never gone

[Chorus]
Oh, Cristina and Ron, their love shines so bright
They're inseparable, like day and night
In each other's hearts, they find pure delight
Una canción de amor, unidos para siempre en su sentir
